= SDL_RenderFillRects =
Use this function to fill some number of rectangles on the current rendering target with the drawing color.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_RenderFillRects(const SDL_Rect** rect,
                        int              count)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''rect'''
|a pointer to an array of destination rectangles of type [[SDL_Rect]]
|-
|'''count'''
|the number of rectangles
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

